Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后  他刪除了所有社交媒體賬號\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He deleted all of his social media accounts after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用別名注冊了一個新賬戶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}set up a new one under an alias
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果你還是找到了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and yet you still found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該防著你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Should I be worried about you?
