Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強奸了一位名叫凡妮莎·哈蒙的警探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He raped a police officer called Vanessa Harmon,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在愛丁堡強奸了一位叫凱瑟琳·麥考利的女子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and he raped a woman called Catherine MacAulay in Edinburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是她們的號碼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here are their numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不相信我  那就跟她們聊聊吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you don't believe me, then talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再作出判斷  你覺得誰說的是真話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then you make up your mind who you think is telling the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們三人  還是安德魯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the three of us or Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不認識你  但是我知道他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, I don't know you, but I know him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他能做出些什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I know what he's capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喜歡聰慧  獨立\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He likes women who are smart, independent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更有挑戰的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}more of a challenge to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿你夠聰明  能多留點神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm hoping you're smart enough to watch your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者至少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠聰明地自己去查一查我跟你說的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}smart enough to check out what I'm telling you for yourself.
