Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是嗎  -她甚至有你那種能看穿人的頭腦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Is she? - Yeah, look, she's even got your see-through head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是女孩的話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's if she is a she.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好  我只是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心不在焉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來后  你一直這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have been since I got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一次出差任務\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Look, it's... it's one more tour of duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就能回家了  不再是珍妮佛大兵了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and then I'm home, right? No more GI Jennifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分娩之前我會回來的  然后我哪也不去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll be back before the birth and then I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. I just miss you, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你騙不了我  妮莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't lie to me, Ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什么事了  你一臉愁容\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's going on? You've got that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-沒事  -聽著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's nothing. - Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以一直問到你受不了為止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can keep asking you, again and again till I drive you crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者你現在就告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or you can just tell me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別問了  好嗎  我沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just leave it, OK, I am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就告訴我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮莎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你變了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你努力想要掩蓋  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've tried to pretend, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想要聽實話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All I'm asking for is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有其他人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is there someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天  不是的  當然不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God, no. Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  到底怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走的這些天里  發生了一些事  但拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}While you were away, something happened, but please...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能  我不想說出口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}please, I can't, I don't want to say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什么事  都沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever it is, it's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以告訴我  怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can tell me. You can tell me, what is it?
