Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盧克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Luke?
