Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你怎么樣  -挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How are you doing? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想問問\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在學校還好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}..How's school, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是撤銷了指控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just because the charges were dropped,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不意味著人們不再討論了  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}doesn't mean people don't talk, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道這對你來說有多不難  但你這樣并不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know how hard it is for you but it's not gonna get any easier -
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別給我什么建議了  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Spare me the advice, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像你有資格說這些話一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like you're in any position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這話什么意思  盧克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What does that mean? Luke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我洗清了罪名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的罪名都洗得干干凈凈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All those charges, not one of them stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你不相信我  好吧  你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you don't believe me, right, you and me...
