Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想談談  勞拉  我還能想干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'I want to talk, Laura. What else would I want?'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你離我遠點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You need to leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在睡覺有點早  不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Bit early to be in bed, isn't it?'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會想我嗎  當你躺在那的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Do you think about me? When you're lying there.'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定想起我了  不是嗎  盡管你不會承認\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'You do, don't you? Even though you wouldn't admit it.'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在立刻給我離開這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You need to get away from here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你和夏洛特聊過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'I know you spoke to Charlotte,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我覺得你才是那個該滾開的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I think you're the one that needs to back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是時候繼續自己的生活了  你不覺得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Time we both got on with our lives, don't you think?'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得你凌駕于所有人和事  是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think you stand above everyone and everything, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得沒人抓得到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That you're untouchable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也只是個人罷了  安德魯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you're just a man, Andrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個惡心脆弱的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A sick, weak man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天你會清醒過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And one day you're gonna wake up
