Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為如果我想占有你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cos if I wanted to have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次占有你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.49,0:20:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不覺得只要我想  隨時都能動手嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}don't you think I could have had you whenever I wanted?
