Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勞拉...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Laura...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那樣的男人就是想控制和羞辱女性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Men like him want to control and humiliate women.
