Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣他就會犯錯  我們就可以把他繩之以法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's when he'll make mistakes, that's when we'll catch him.
