Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.72,0:25:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.86,0:25:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Er, here.
