Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.97,0:37:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西爾維婭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sylvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.16,0:37:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是安德魯的朋友  勞拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a friend of Andrew's. Laura.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.07,0:37:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.87,0:37:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有訪客真好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How nice to have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.17,0:37:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德魯從來不帶客人來  是吧  米婭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andrew never brings visitors here, does he, Mia?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.84,0:37:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-從來沒  -安德魯叫我來幫他取東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No, never. - Andrew asked me to pick something up for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.60,0:37:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有東西存在這里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's got some stuff stored here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.28,0:37:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本應該幾天前來拿的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was supposed to collect it a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.06,0:37:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.30,0:37:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  當然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.36,0:37:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.69,0:37:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.53,0:38:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.23,0:38:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  我會盡量快點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thanks. I'll try and be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.48,0:38:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我是米婭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello. It's Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.54,0:39:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你找到了嗎  你有沒有...  -有  謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Do you have everything? Did you find - Yes, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.29,0:39:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得走了  謝謝你們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got to run. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.37,0:40:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs16\i1}凡妮莎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.54,0:41:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她在里邊很生氣  -好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- She's pretty upset in there. - OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.67,0:41:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-天啊  終于  -真抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Oh, God. Finally. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.43,0:41:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒值班  我得走程序進來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wasn't on duty. I had to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.60,0:41:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給凡妮莎打電話卻直接進語音信息了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I called Vanessa but her phone goes straight to voicemail.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.27,0:41:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為有了這發現  你們會行動快一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'd think people would move quicker after what I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.53,0:41:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前臺告訴我錄像的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The front desk told me about the recordings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.96,0:42:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  那個...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, it's erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.78,0:42:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.32,0:42:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都沒膽量去看  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I could barely bring myself to look, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.25,0:42:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在里邊  還有凡妮莎  還有...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I'm in there, and...Vanessa and...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.84,0:42:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我算了算  至少還有其他15個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I counted at least 15 others.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.09,0:42:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15位和我有同樣遭遇的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}15 women just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.96,0:42:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,17\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}17.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.95,0:42:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,技術人員說是17位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The tech guys tell me 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.01,0:42:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且安德魯·厄拉姆可以很清晰地被辨認出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And Andrew Earlham is clearly identifiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.58,0:42:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他將會進去很長時間  尼爾森小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's going away, Miss Nielson, for a really, really long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.64,0:42:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前也聽過這話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.30,0:42:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們讓你進了房子  他們讓你搜索小屋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They let you into the house. They let you search the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.94,0:42:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到的一切都會成為證據\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everything you found is going into evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.51,0:42:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.98,0:43:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.08,0:43:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.00,0:43:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在正去抓捕他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're picking him up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.08,0:43:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要找安德魯·厄拉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're looking for Andrew Earlham.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.09,0:43:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-找我爸爸干什么  -我們有逮捕令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What do you want with my dad? - We have a warrant for his arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.69,0:43:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.41,0:44:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs16\i1}強奸嫌疑犯\N警察尋求幫助尋找肯特強奸嫌疑犯
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.60,0:44:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后  雖然進行了三周的搜尋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'And, finally, despite three weeks of searching,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.30,0:44:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察依然無法找到安德魯·厄拉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the police are no closer to finding Andrew Earlham,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.71,0:44:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此人與多項強奸指控有關\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}who is wanted in connection with a number of rape allegations.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.96,0:44:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厄拉姆先生  廣山醫院的心胸外科醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mr Earlham, a cardiothoracic surgeon at Broadhill Hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.89,0:44:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是近幾個月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has been the subject of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.08,0:44:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩起調查的主要對象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}two separate investigations in recent months,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.67,0:44:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是都沒有最終定罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but neither case led to prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.18,0:44:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾周前發布了一張針對厄拉姆先生的逮捕令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Several weeks ago, a warrant was issued for Mr Earlham's arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.72,0:44:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后不久  他幾年前性侵對象的錄像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, shortly after, recordings of his alleged sexual assaults
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.66,0:44:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被泄露給了媒體\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}dating back years, were leaked to the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.49,0:44:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方尋求任何線索 只要關于厄拉姆先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Police ask that anyone with information on Mr Earlham
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.09,0:44:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是他目前的所在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}or his whereabouts come forward.'
